2864673902287221905.Text: I gave Han-Ammu the War Axe of Airan-Ammu and made a little speech about strength and symbols and responsibility. I believe he has taken the lesson to heart, and will consider accepting his responsibilities as ashkhan, and consider naming me Nerevarine. But he says he doesn't need the axe, and that I should keep it for myself.
